  m_text: A wave is a medium where sound propagates without carrying over the matter
    where it moves. Waves do not only carry sounds, however. Different waves propagate
    different things, such as electrical signals, light, and so on. Such a wave is
    a mechanical wave.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
